      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:52:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚航空公司因燃料短缺取消航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/colombian-government-says-aviation-fuel-shortage-has-been-fixed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚最大的航空公司哥伦比亚航空表示正在限制机票销售，而拉美航空集团则因航空燃油短缺取消了该国的一些航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/colombian-government-says-aviation-fuel-shortage-has-been-fixed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:36:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称移民拘留中心虐待现象普遍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/migrants-abused-in-ice-detention-centers-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据法律和人权组织联盟周一发布的报告，关押在路易斯安那州九个拘留中心的移民经常遭受符合酷刑法律定义的侵犯人权行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/migrants-abused-in-ice-detention-centers-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 13:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>失业率飙升 加拿大将限制外国工人涌入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/canada-to-restrict-access-to-low-wage-foreign-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将限制一项允许公司招募低薪外国劳工的计划，此前政府因让该计划发展过快以及未能阻止对临时工的虐待而受到批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/canada-to-restrict-access-to-low-wage-foreign-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大将对中国电动汽车和钢铁征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/canada-to-hit-china-with-tariffs-on-electric-vehicles-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将对中国制造的电动汽车、铝和钢铁征收新的关税，与西方盟友站在一起并采取措施保护国内制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/canada-to-hit-china-with-tariffs-on-electric-vehicles-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 11:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
