      <title>加纳总统候选人支持严厉的反 LGBTQ 法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统支持制定严厉的反 LGBTQ 法律的计划，以争取保守派选民的支持，从而成为这个西非国家的下一任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
